Wait (script event)
===================

Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [Game\_class.html game class] type [Thread\_(scripting).html idThread], accessible via [Scripting\_basics.html\#sys sys] identifier.

Description
-----------

Suspends execution of the current thread for the given number of seconds.

Usage
-----

*[Data\_types.html\#void void]* wait( *[Data\_types.html\#float float]* **time** )

Parameters
----------

-   [time] - The duration in seconds to suspend execution.

